@startuml
title Dataflow: Web UI Login & Auth State

autonumber
skinparam Style strictuml

actor "User" as user
participant "Login Page" as page
participant "useAuth (Hook)" as hook
participant "IdentityClient" as client
participant "Identity Service" as api

user -> page : Enter credentials & Submit
page -> hook : login(email, password)
hook -> client : login()
client -> api : POST /identity/authentication/login

api --[#green]> client : 200 OK (Set-Cookie: smap_auth_token)
note right: Cookie is HttpOnly (Secure)

client --> hook : Return User Info
hook -> hook : Update AuthContext (setUser)
hook --> page : Redirect to /projects
page --> user : Show Dashboard
@enduml